{"tid":682918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侍應遭前妻追斬　遺50米血路","createTime":"2018-05-29T08:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T09:45:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4518a4b591a5d9a8c882a5ed0d66d572bce9c852","tid":682918,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180529/20404417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F20404417&d=9Dv2KEQJ5IsBy%2B2prVFR%2FaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=a8c4ce8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F20404417&h=95e1b8b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180529/20404417</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月29日 <br />\n<br />\n侍應遭前妻追斬　遺50米血路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180529/large/a0904a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180529%2Flarge%2Fa0904a.gif&h=30e362b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■男子捱斬後逃跑，神色慌張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名已離婚女子昨晨到前夫位於大角嘴工作的餐廳傾談，其間疑因爭奪子女撫養權問題起爭執，女子情緒激動拿出利刀斬傷前夫，事主手部受傷，淌血逃走約50米後不支倒地，被經過的救護車發現送院，涉案女子潛逃半日後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女疑犯被捕<br />\n<br />\n被斬傷男子姓李（30歲），與姓肖（40歲）前妻育有一名女兒。李於大角嘴大全街一間餐廳任兼職侍應約半年，昨晨約6時開始上班。至早上約9時半，前妻到來找他傾談，事主圍裙未除便步出店外。據悉雙方為子女的撫養權問題越吵越烈，前妻情緒激動下突取出利刀揮舞，事主手部受傷。<br />\n<br />\n根據閉路電視片段，身穿圍裙的男事主滿手鮮血，一臉驚慌地沿大全街逃跑，一名疑是其前妻的長髮女子手持大袋緊追其後，男事主急步逃走，前妻未能追及，稍後橫過馬路逃去。<br />\n<br />\n事主負傷由大全街往大角嘴道方向逃走，右轉入大政街再橫過埃華街，走了約50米後倒地。一輛救護車經過現場，救護員發現事主手部淌血，立即停車施救，並將他送院治理。現場遺下血路，警方追緝半日後於旺角區拘捕涉案女子。<br />\n<br />\n■記者文兆麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n拾荒者哭訴食環無情　回收商呃秤<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n醉男與妻嗌交跳海　EU攬水泡救<br />\n<br />\n【天眼直擊】狠妻刺前夫片段曝光 掌摑後再出利剪"},{"pid":"df3dca1476607d83d16600e049e4300ed1c16d28","tid":682918,"uid":147871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"一輛救護車經過現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fc1825917d2fa3b0d59d6786c02b55fea1c534","tid":682918,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"支那女人？"},{"pid":"16b8280bf92cede0c0557fcf3bc3b6a2031c88b5","tid":682918,"uid":43061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男30歲 女40歲"},{"pid":"1069f22ce19450077189555ed10f6a4afe0de8fa","tid":682918,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"姓肖"},{"pid":"5c0b558796581dcef9cc868574f355cfcb1a7532","tid":682918,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:13:03.000Z","msg":"近排好多 斬兩單<br />\n強水一單"},{"pid":"25929b47c13ced4b82083aedeb84f59fc9b7b044","tid":682918,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b8280bf92cede0c0557fcf3bc3b6a2031c88b5","tid":682918,"uid":43061,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男30歲 女40歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:21:10.000Z","msg":"連登仔最鐘意嘅姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de337a35095bbafdd5938b77b2e994ab4789bfa4","tid":682918,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"姓肖"},{"pid":"38f4c9f6a2fd26055c073e6b92c76f76e5e5fabe","tid":682918,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de337a35095bbafdd5938b77b2e994ab4789bfa4","tid":682918,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"姓肖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"友"},{"pid":"7fe58355be232a7cbb3b516fb51d8ceee0882479"